****************************************************************************************************************************************************************************

MALWARE ANALYSIS:-This is an harder section of Cybersecurity where You should need the good knowledge regarding the system internals,assembly,debugging and programming
Type:-
1)STATIC:-analysing without executing the malware
2)DYNAMIC:-analysing the malware while execution
NOTE:-FOR MALWARE ANALYSIS YOU SHOULD HAVE A SEPERATE ENVIORNMENT BEACUSE IT IS VERY DANGEROUS AT THAT TIME !!!!You should run the virus or malware at a different VM
And that vm must be cut off with the internet !!!
EG:-AN ARTICLE FOR SEPERATE VM'S WITH TOOLS FOR MALWARE ANALYSIS

https://github.com/fireeye/flare-vm

Credits:-FireEye
This vm consist of all tools that are required for an malware analyst 


