RED TEAMING:-
What is red teaming??
A red team may be a contracted external party or an internal group that uses strategies to encourage an outsider perspective...
Requires good offensive techniques and to know good knowledge regarding red teaming tools....
Phases:-
1)Reconnaisance aka information gatherng
Tools:-
OPENVAS
NIKTO
MALTEGO
SHODAN

2)Weponization:-Weaponization is the process of building and using tools for attacking a target, by taking into account information gathered 
from the reconnaisance phase.
Tools:-
Metasploit
Invoke-Obfustication
Veil

3)Delivery and exploitation:-
Tools:-
Gophish
Hashcat
BEEF

4)Privilege escalation:-
Tools:-
PowerUp
BeRoot

5)Lateral Movement:-
One of the phases of the APT(Advance Persistent Threat) life cycle, and it makes its way into red team operations as well.
Tools:-
LaZagne

6)Control and Control:-
Tools:-
EvilURL
Empire Project


7)Exfiltrate and complete:-
This is where manipulations of the target system are performed in order to achieve the objective of the operation.
Tools:-
Det
Powershell RAT


******************************************************************************************************************************************************************************

